{"tid":1631121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再out focus ok?","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:38.000Z","uid":188576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"150cd2243d36964f29de3b6b1c5f4519c616eb99","tid":1631121,"uid":188576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺呢兩日都係一面倒話示威者乜乜乜？<br />\n<br />\n黑警實彈射人呢？<br />\n休班警實彈射人呢？<br />\n唔好淨係講神獸<br />\n私了我絕對讚成，但唔該諗返提出私了其中一個原因係黑警選擇性執法，我哋先要無奈咁做<br />\n呢一樣先係我地要攻嘅位<br />\n<br />\n藍絲之爭只係人民同人民嘅爭鬥，國際上冇人想知<br />\n麻煩大家對準返，而家係要制裁黑警<br />\n<br />\n新蒲崗暗角打人2.0冇人提？<br />\n細路女驚到震哂冇人提？<br />\n上街只係破壞中資而無訴求？<br />\n<br />\n麻煩唔好走焦<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好再問「咁做割唔割」<br />\n到底係幾撚無安全感呀？<br />\n都未撚出核彈，驚乜？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我為大家破壞而不盜竊感到自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0fb6f23c2f61633d4cfa8aa8273d97389bee72","tid":1631121,"uid":188576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ced0309e81614594c818c219af05d71b349c8d0f","tid":1631121,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=c8282cf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"}]}